 vendor development program includes an intensive fourandahalfday workshop designed to give select high potential minority and womenowned companies the tools to better succeed and sustain growth in the retail industry to apply for the program often called “lifechanging” by participants review the eligibility requirements and submit your application before the deadline and the program is free yes you read that right to learn more see the program overview and read what past participants have to say you can also explore success stories of past workshop participants and learn more about the impact it’s had on their businesses through a series of video interviews find out what applying for the workshop at macy’s could do for your business we’re accepting applications until  pm est on january   apply now homeaboutbusiness of fashioneligibilityapplybuzzfaqcontact  macy’s inc  west seventh st cincinnati oh  all rights reserved review the macysinccom privacy policy and legal notice macys inc  company profile from hoover’s  db hoovers menu buy reports  lists how it works united states united kingdom   login company people industry search db hoovers company  people  industry login avention onesource is now db hoovers login here for access to db hoovers db datavision db business browser and isell login for customers of hoovers prior to march   login call   chat software by boldchat start free trial call   chat software by boldchat start free trial search the db hoovers database company company people industry home company information company search company overview  profile company profile information for sales preparation marketing contacts competition revenue  financial available products company report nonstore retail industry report clothing stores industry report shoe stores industry report department stores industry report furniture stores industry report home furniture  housewares stores industry report internet  mailorder retail industry report retail sector industry re